984
01:05:45,108 --> 01:05:47,944
相信我 我懂 我經歷過
{\fs12}Trust me, I know. I've been there.

985
01:06:34,157 --> 01:06:35,408
感覺到了嗎
{\fs12}Feel her?

986
01:06:36,993 --> 01:06:37,994
是
{\fs12}Yeah.

987
01:06:39,245 --> 01:06:41,831
德拉戈的精彩表現讓所有質疑都煙消雲散
{\fs12}Highlights of Drago silencing critics tonight

988
01:06:41,915 --> 01:06:44,667
