997
01:07:04,187 --> 01:07:07,357
如果他不跟你打呢 那他就不算拳王
{\fs12}And if he doesn't fight you? - Then he's no champion.

998
01:07:07,482 --> 01:07:11,236
你聽到了嗎 阿多尼斯 這可是赤裸裸的挑戰
{\fs12}There you have it, Adonis. Challenge is on the table.

999
01:07:21,051 --> 01:07:22,512
我們非常為你驕傲

1000
01:07:23,488 --> 01:07:24,682
敬你 維克托

1001
01:07:24,708 --> 01:07:26,205
敬伊凡 敬你們

1002
01:07:26,578 --> 01:07:27,946
願你的成功

1003
01:07:28,687 --> 01:07:31,340
能重現俄羅斯拳壇昔日的輝煌

1004
01:07:31,757 --> 01:07:33,261
你是我們的希望

1005
01:07:33,281 --> 01:07:34,019
維克托

1006
01:07:35,238 --> 01:07:36,656
請收下這份禮物

1007
01:07:51,384 --> 01:07:55,343
<i>德拉戈</i>

1008
01:07:59,176 --> 01:08:00,760
現在你們要做的

1009
01:08:00,785 --> 01:08:04,047
就是趁這次比賽一舉奪下金腰帶 懂嗎

1010
01:08:27,593 --> 01:08:28,618
坐吧

1011
01:08:42,913 --> 01:08:44,504
你好 維克托

1012
01:08:49,181 --> 01:08:51,947
相信你一定覺得非常自豪吧

1013
01:09:08,269 --> 01:09:09,562
維克托
{\fs12}Viktor!

1014
01:09:10,461 --> 01:09:13,532
堶惆漕リH是為了我們專程到這兒來的

1015
01:09:14,312 --> 01:09:14,962
為了你而來的

1016
01:09:14,988 --> 01:09:16,188
堶惆漕リH嗎

1017
01:09:17,643 --> 01:09:19,333
堶惆漕リH怎麼對你的

1018
01:09:19,335 --> 01:09:20,750
他們當年把你趕走了

1019
01:09:21,167 --> 01:09:23,124
我們為什麼非要到這堥

1020
01:09:23,127 --> 01:09:24,255
這是為了將來

1021
01:09:24,258 --> 01:09:26,736
我根本都不算認識那個女人

1022
01:09:26,739 --> 01:09:28,495
我也巴不得不認識她 維克托

1023
01:09:28,521 --> 01:09:30,261
她當年拋棄了你

1024
01:09:30,264 --> 01:09:31,305
他們都是

1025
01:09:31,308 --> 01:09:32,871
那些人都把你給拋棄了

1026
01:09:32,873 --> 01:09:33,959
他們還羞辱你

1027
01:09:33,963 --> 01:09:35,946
是我輸了比賽

1028
01:09:38,663 --> 01:09:40,472
我當年輸了比賽

1029
01:09:40,621 --> 01:09:42,602
但你不會再輸下去了

1030
01:09:53,765 --> 01:09:57,394
<i>德爾斐拳擊學院</i>

1031
01:10:09,080 --> 01:10:10,081
怎麼了
{\fs12}What's good?

1032
01:10:10,415 --> 01:10:12,792
好久不見 忙什麼呢
{\fs12}Just maintaining, man. Long time no see, what's up?

1033
01:10:13,167 --> 01:10:18,089
也沒什麼事 就是瞎忙 是嗎 裝修 待產
{\fs12}Nothing, man. Just been caught up. You know, the house, the baby.

1034
01:10:18,548 --> 01:10:19,590
你知道多麻煩
{\fs12}You know how it is.

1035
01:10:19,716 --> 01:10:21,008
好吧 比安卡好嗎
{\fs12}Yeah? How Bianca doing?

1036
01:10:21,843 --> 01:10:24,220
她挺好 挺好
{\fs12}She's good. She's good.

1037
01:10:24,721 --> 01:10:26,305
好
{\fs12}Good, good, good.

1038
01:10:27,849 --> 01:10:30,268
其實我一直很想聯繫你 兄弟
{\fs12}Listen, man, I've been meaning to hit you up, though.

1039
01:10:31,394 --> 01:10:33,604
理事會想知道我們下一場比賽跟誰打
{\fs12}Commissioner wanna know who we plan to fight next.

1040
01:10:34,188 --> 01:10:36,107
就算不跟德拉戈打
{\fs12}You ain't got to fight Drago,

1041
01:10:36,274 --> 01:10:38,401
你也得跟別人打
{\fs12}but you got to fight someone.

1042
01:10:38,985 --> 01:10:40,653
你得守住金腰帶
{\fs12}You got to defend the belt.

1043
01:10:41,696 --> 01:10:43,698
不然它就要被收回去了
{\fs12}Otherwise, it's gonna be vacated.

1044
01:10:46,284 --> 01:10:49,454
你知道 我能幫你 選個好打一點的對手
{\fs12}I could set up a little, you know, tune-up fight, kind of.

1045
01:10:56,377 --> 01:10:57,378
算了 這樣吧
{\fs12}No. You know what, man?

1046
01:10:57,462 --> 01:10:58,588
你現在還是別操心這些事了
{\fs12}Don't worry about none of that right now.

1047
01:10:58,671 --> 01:11:01,215
就進來玩會兒吧
{\fs12}Listen, just come on inside.

1048
01:11:01,424 --> 01:11:03,384
打打沙包 熱熱身
{\fs12}Hit the bag, man, warm up.

1049
01:11:04,427 --> 01:11:05,720
好
{\fs12}Yeah.

1050
01:11:05,887 --> 01:11:09,015
我先去拿裝備 然後再進去找你
{\fs12}Yeah, I'm gonna grab my stuff, and I'm gonna meet you in there.

1051
01:11:11,684 --> 01:11:13,269
好吧 兄弟
{\fs12}All right, man.

1052
01:11:23,446 --> 01:11:25,198
用全身的重量出拳
{\fs12}Put your body weight into that glove.

1053
01:11:25,364 --> 01:11:27,200
這就對了 上前一步
{\fs12}There you go. Lean in it.

1054
01:11:38,920 --> 01:11:41,464
是啊 我都給你打了無數個電話了
{\fs12}Yeah, I called you, like, a thousand times.

1055
01:11:42,799 --> 01:11:44,509
是 我家燈壞了
{\fs12}Yeah, it's about the light.

1056
01:11:45,718 --> 01:11:46,803
壞了多久啊
{\fs12}How long?

1057
01:11:46,969 --> 01:11:49,347
仔細算算 有好幾年了吧
{\fs12}You want to be specific? Couple years.

1058
01:11:49,514 --> 01:11:50,598
對
{\fs12}Yeah.

1059
01:11:50,765 --> 01:11:53,559
只是擰個燈泡而已 用得了幾個人
{\fs12}I mean, how many guys does it take to screw in a light bulb?

1060
01:11:55,561 --> 01:11:56,979
我可沒開玩笑
{\fs12}I'm not joking.

1061
01:11:57,004 --> 01:11:58,748
<i>瑪麗·安·奎迪寄
洛奇·巴爾博亞收</i>

1062
01:11:58,773 --> 01:12:00,316
我再打給你們好嗎
{\fs12}Can I call you guys back?

1063
01:12:00,817 --> 01:12:02,026
行
{\fs12}Yeah.

1064
01:12:10,114 --> 01:12:10,922
什麼

1065
01:12:11,246 --> 01:12:14,057
<i>他仍然需要你
瑪麗·安</i>

1066
01:12:41,607 --> 01:12:42,859
媽
{\fs12}Hey, Ma.

1067
01:12:44,861 --> 01:12:46,028
媽
{\fs12}Ma.

1068
01:12:59,709 --> 01:13:00,751
媽媽
{\fs12}Hey, Ma.

1069
01:13:04,672 --> 01:13:05,965
最近好嗎 小子
{\fs12}How you doing, kid?

1070
01:13:07,842 --> 01:13:09,135
你過來幹什麼
{\fs12}What are you doing here?

1071
01:13:09,302 --> 01:13:10,595
希望你別介意
{\fs12}I hope you don't mind,

1072
01:13:10,678 --> 01:13:14,307
是你媽媽請我過來的 因為她非常擔心你
{\fs12}your mom asked if I would come out 'cause she's worried about you.

1073
01:13:17,268 --> 01:13:18,811
我也是
{\fs12}I am, too.

1074
01:13:19,437 --> 01:13:20,813
我很好
{\fs12}I'm good.

1075
01:13:23,399 --> 01:13:24,859
你不用大老遠過來一趟
{\fs12}You didn't have to come all this way.

1076
01:13:25,026 --> 01:13:26,193
我坐火車來的
{\fs12}By train.

1077
01:13:27,028 --> 01:13:29,572
在車上待了三天
{\fs12}Three days on a train.

1078
01:13:30,740 --> 01:13:33,034
也挺好 你知道 我有思考的時間了
{\fs12}It's all right, you know, gives you time to think.

1079
01:13:33,200 --> 01:13:37,538
可以看著一處處風景 像明信片一樣從窗外閃過
{\fs12}And you watch all these places whipping by the windows like postcards.

1080
01:13:37,705 --> 01:13:39,498
也是一種不錯的經歷
{\fs12}It's quite an experience.

1081
01:13:39,665 --> 01:13:41,834
是 你開心就好
{\fs12}Yeah, I mean, if you say so.

1082
01:13:42,001 --> 01:13:43,586
是 真挺好
{\fs12}Yeah, it was nice.

1083
01:13:44,921 --> 01:13:46,380
這個房間太棒了
{\fs12}This is wonderful.

1084
01:13:46,547 --> 01:13:49,759
這兒怎麼能有這麼多的獎盃呢
{\fs12}How you have all this out here.

1085
01:13:50,843 --> 01:13:52,678
你也能有這麼多獎盃
{\fs12}You could have the same.

1086
01:13:53,596 --> 01:13:55,348
是嗎 我可沒有自信
{\fs12}Yeah, I wouldn't say that.

1087
01:13:55,514 --> 01:13:58,100
我說的不只是榮譽
{\fs12}I mean, not just the shiny stuff,

1088
01:13:58,893 --> 01:14:00,353
有些東西更有價值
{\fs12}but the better stuff.

1089
01:14:02,521 --> 01:14:03,814
比如更好的人生
{\fs12}Have a better life.

1090
01:14:07,568 --> 01:14:09,278
做更好的人
{\fs12}Be a better man.

1091
01:14:11,656 --> 01:14:14,867
知道嗎 我其實一直在想 你之前質問我說
{\fs12}You know, I was thinking about what you were saying about

1092
01:14:14,992 --> 01:14:18,579
我是不是覺得留在原地守著你就是在犯傻
{\fs12}what smart decisions have I made lately.

1093
01:14:22,166 --> 01:14:24,126
但沒想出個結果
{\fs12}Couldn't think of many.

1094
01:14:26,087 --> 01:14:29,966
跟你說我兒子的兒子 就是我的親孫子
{\fs12}You know, I wasn't even there when my son's son,

1095
01:14:32,009 --> 01:14:33,302
他出生時
{\fs12}my grandson,

1096
01:14:34,053 --> 01:14:35,262
我沒去
{\fs12}was born.

1097
01:14:36,305 --> 01:14:40,559
他現在可能都已經長這麼高了
{\fs12}I mean, he's like that tall now probably.

1098
01:14:40,726 --> 01:14:43,396
我卻還不認識他 他也不認識我
{\fs12}I don't even know him. He doesn't know me.

1099
01:14:46,691 --> 01:14:48,401
真的很可悲
{\fs12}It's pathetic.

1100
01:14:49,735 --> 01:14:51,445
那幹嗎不給他
{\fs12}Well, why won't you just

1101
01:14:53,030 --> 01:14:54,198
打電話
{\fs12}call him?

1102
01:14:55,282 --> 01:14:57,493
設那麼容易 你懂嗎
{\fs12}It ain't that easy, you know...

1103
01:14:59,996 --> 01:15:00,997
聽著
{\fs12}Listen,

1104
01:15:01,205 --> 01:15:04,667
我不希望你重蹈覆轍 犯我犯過的錯
{\fs12}I don't want you making the same mistakes I made.

1105
01:15:05,501 --> 01:15:07,211
你懂我意思嗎
{\fs12}You know what I mean?

1106
01:15:10,089 --> 01:15:12,008
所以你要問問你自己
{\fs12}So, you got to ask yourself,

1107
01:15:13,050 --> 01:15:15,136
到底什麼東西才是有價值的
{\fs12}what's the valuable stuff?

1108
01:15:15,720 --> 01:15:17,930
我以前也問過你類似的問題
{\fs12}It's like I asked you before.

1109
01:15:18,764 --> 01:15:21,350
你一路奮戰到底是為了什麼
{\fs12}What were you really fighting for?

1110
01:15:23,602 --> 01:15:24,979
我之前很怕
{\fs12}I was afraid.

1111
01:15:28,399 --> 01:15:29,734
榮譽
{\fs12}Of this.

1112
01:15:33,320 --> 01:15:34,697
怕別人的期待
{\fs12}Expectations.

1113
01:15:35,740 --> 01:15:37,199
怕當拳王
{\fs12}Being the champ.

1114
01:15:39,702 --> 01:15:42,705
我怕我自己達不到爸爸的高度
{\fs12}I was scared I couldn't do what he couldn't.

1115
01:15:45,166 --> 01:15:46,500
挺奇怪的
{\fs12}It's weird.

1116
01:15:48,919 --> 01:15:51,130
我曾覺得他是我的一部分
{\fs12}I used to feel like he was a part of me.

1117
01:15:52,715 --> 01:15:54,925
現在我卻聽不到他的召喚了
{\fs12}Now I can't hear him, or that thing,

1118
01:15:55,634 --> 01:15:57,845
我聽不到他讓我上拳台奮戰
{\fs12}that thing that tells me to get in the ring.

1119
01:15:58,679 --> 01:16:00,931
要腳下不停 一直舉著拳頭
{\fs12}Move my feet, keep my hands up.

1120
01:16:01,098 --> 01:16:03,267
打倒所有阻擋我的東西
{\fs12}Hit anything that gets in my way.

1121
01:16:07,730 --> 01:16:09,523
我再也聽不到了
{\fs12}I can't hear it anymore.

1122
01:16:17,531 --> 01:16:19,617
我都不知道我怎麼輸的
{\fs12}I don't even know how I lost.

1123
01:16:19,784 --> 01:16:21,744
你這麼想就不對
{\fs12}Your mind wasn't right.

1124
01:16:24,246 --> 01:16:28,167
其實你天生就不適合走爸爸這樣傳奇的路線
{\fs12}And your natural style just won't work with a guy that big.

1125
01:16:36,675 --> 01:16:38,511
那我更適合你的路線嗎
{\fs12}You saying yours was better?

1126
01:16:39,512 --> 01:16:41,180
我贏過 不是嗎
{\fs12}I won, didn't I?

1127
01:16:48,229 --> 01:16:50,856
見到你真好 我也很開心見到你
{\fs12}Good seeing you, Unc. - Great to see you, too.

1128
01:16:51,524 --> 01:16:53,025
我之前跟你媽媽仔細聊過一陣 她說
{\fs12}I was talking with your mother,

1129
01:16:53,109 --> 01:16:58,489
你給你的孩子起了個名字叫做阿
{\fs12}and she says you came up with this name for the child.

1130
01:16:58,656 --> 01:16:59,865
阿瑪拉
{\fs12}Amara. - Amara.

1131
01:16:59,990 --> 01:17:01,033
是 好
{\fs12}Yeah. - Yeah.

1132
01:17:01,283 --> 01:17:02,284
有什麼問題嗎
{\fs12}Why, what's wrong with that?

1133
01:17:02,368 --> 01:17:05,412
不 沒事 這名字很好聽 就是有點不好念
{\fs12}No, it's a beautiful name, but it's kind of complicated.

1134
01:17:05,496 --> 01:17:07,039
為什麼不起一個能讓人
{\fs12}Why don't you think about something,

1135
01:17:07,123 --> 01:17:09,291
至少能讓我念得順口點的
{\fs12}at least I would, a little simpler to say,

1136
01:17:09,375 --> 01:17:12,628
比如貝姬或者凱特之類的
{\fs12}like "Becky" or "Cate," something like that.

1137
01:17:12,711 --> 01:17:13,838
凱特·奎迪
{\fs12}Cate Creed?

1138
01:17:13,921 --> 01:17:15,923
凱特·奎迪 雙C開頭 挺好記
{\fs12}Cate Creed. Two "C's." Easy to remember.

1139
01:17:16,006 --> 01:17:17,716
你知道黑人不起這種名字吧
{\fs12}You do know she's gonna be black, right?

1140
01:17:18,008 --> 01:17:19,927
對啊 我給忘了
{\fs12}Oh, that's right, I forgot.

1141
01:17:21,345 --> 01:17:22,596
好吧
{\fs12}Okay.

1142
01:17:23,514 --> 01:17:25,349
喂 媽 好吧
{\fs12}Hey, Ma. - Yeah.

1143
01:17:27,226 --> 01:17:28,644
等等 現在嗎
{\fs12}Wait, right now?

1144
01:17:30,563 --> 01:17:31,939
放鬆點 好的
{\fs12}Relax. - Okay.

1145
01:17:32,022 --> 01:17:34,066
什麼事都不會有
{\fs12}Everything's gonna be fine. - Mmm-hmm.

1146
01:17:34,900 --> 01:17:37,611
你就是到這堥茬郎o的 懂嗎 你就做這個
{\fs12}You just got to be there for her, okay? That's your job.

1147
01:17:37,695 --> 01:17:38,779
我明白
{\fs12}I got you, I got you.

1148
01:17:38,863 --> 01:17:40,322
你記好
